OpenStreetMaps Visualization

Kan Dai

Feb 12, 2020

1 Overview

使用osmdata包获得地图上的街道数据, 并制作图像. 可以参考: * https://rpubs.com/rubenfbc/openstreetmap

2 Environmental Setup

library(osmdata)
library(tidyverse)

4 检索数据信息

4.1 设置北京市范围

# Beijing area
area_min <- c(116.0, 39.7)
area_max <- c(116.8, 40.1)
area_df <- as.matrix(data.frame(min=area_min, max=area_max))
row.names(area_df) <- c("x","y")

4.2 获得公路主干道数据

area_highway <- area_df %>% opq() %>%
  add_osm_feature(key = "highway", 
                  value = c("road", "motorway", "primary")) %>%
  osmdata_sf()

area_highway
Object of class 'osmdata' with:
                 $bbox : 39.7,116,40.1,116.8
        $overpass_call : The call submitted to the overpass API
                 $meta : metadata including timestamp and version numbers
           $osm_points : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 38221 points
            $osm_lines : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 6868 linestrings
         $osm_polygons : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 10 polygons
       $osm_multilines : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 2 multilinestrings
    $osm_multipolygons : NULL
ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = area_highway$osm_lines,
          inherit.aes = FALSE,
          color = "darkgrey",
          size = .4,
          alpha = .8)+
  coord_sf(xlim = c(area_min[1], area_max[1]),  ylim = c(area_min[2], area_max[2]), expand = FALSE) +
  theme_void() +
  labs(title = "Beijing", subtitle = "Beijing highway")

4.3 获得公路支干道数据

area_highway_sub <- area_df %>% opq() %>%
  add_osm_feature(key = "highway", 
                  value = c("secondary","tertiary")) %>%
  osmdata_sf()

                 $bbox : 39.7,116,40.1,116.8

4.4 获得河道数据

area_waterway <- area_df %>% opq() %>%
  add_osm_feature(key = "waterway", 
                  value = c("river")) %>%
  osmdata_sf()
area_waterway
Object of class 'osmdata' with:
                 $bbox : 39.7,116,40.1,116.8
        $overpass_call : The call submitted to the overpass API
                 $meta : metadata including timestamp and version numbers
           $osm_points : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 7646 points
            $osm_lines : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 174 linestrings
         $osm_polygons : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 0 polygons
       $osm_multilines : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 1 multilinestrings
    $osm_multipolygons : NULL
ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = area_highway_sub$osm_lines,
          inherit.aes = FALSE,
          color = "grey40",
          size = .1,
          alpha = .8)+
  geom_sf(data = area_highway$osm_lines,
          inherit.aes = FALSE,
          color = "springgreen",
          size = .4,
          alpha = .8)+
  geom_sf(data = area_waterway$osm_lines,
          inherit.aes = FALSE,
          color = "lightblue",
          size = .2,
          alpha = .8) +
  coord_sf(xlim=c(area_min[1], area_max[1]),  ylim=c(area_min[2], area_max[2]), expand = FALSE) +
  theme_void() +
  labs(title = "Beijing") +
  theme(plot.background = element_rect(fill = "grey10"),
        plot.title = element_text(colour = "white"))
